{"tid":1479092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【全世界聽住：818   一 定 要full gear！！】","createTime":"2019-08-16T18:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T18:29:06.000Z","uid":105497,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e5b6a31b1ebe5aa256f210c727f8e50870b275b","tid":1479092,"uid":105497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:21:09.000Z","msg":"818 遊行都一定要full gear<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">至少豬嘴、眼罩、頭盔，缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔係話要撩交打<br />\n818其實真係應該純和理非<br />\n同時超級多人（616級數）<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">都係一定要full gear、著黑衫</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n原因好簡單，唔係因為要撩交打<br />\n（full gear根本就唔等於暴力 咁樣劃等號既人真係唔該收收皮先）<br />\n<br />\n1. 自從政府交曬成個香港俾班狗管之後，香港就無安全而言<br />\n乜都無做過既，可以俾狗一槍打到殘廢，差一丁點就會爆頭死<br />\n去買書既13歲中學妹妹可以拉佢非法集結<br />\n行落街會無啦啦食催淚彈<br />\n港鐵站都可以變毒氣室<br />\n連喺屋企嘆冷氣既柴柴都會食到煙搞到好舒服（條片勁心噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得<br />\n要搞818既原因<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係因為我地要一個安全、自由而且民主既屋企</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而818如果勁多人<br />\n包括和理非到不得了既朋友都是fullgear（或者最少係豬嘴、眼罩、頭盔和黑衣）<br />\n就係最能夠表達呢個訴求既畫面<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n而且過百萬人既和理非遊行當中<br />\n有大量係fullgear咁行既<br />\n國務關注度都一定會好大</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2.既然有狗既地方就有暴力<br />\n就有手足會死既風險<br />\n你永遠唔知818班狗會唔會又發癲（明知群情咁淘湧都反對遊行，真係有撚病架班狗）<br />\n當然後點都保護左自己先啦<br />\n自己唔衝、唔主動撩交打係一回事<br />\n預備好最壞狀況又係另一回事<br />\n老閪都要做最壞打算<br />\n保護好自己<br />\n<br />\n記住，如果因為你無gear而遇到tg放題<br />\n好大機會會係你身邊既手足<br />\n冒住生命危險除個豬嘴俾你戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶full gear唔單止係保護自己<br />\n都係保護緊身邊既手足<br />\n<br />\n總之<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">818和理非<br />\n個個都要出</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818 full gear . <br />\n818 full gear<br />\n818 full gear</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n818 full gear維園見</span>"},{"pid":"9513450c94fccf950bf87e1a6a6285b920fa2600","tid":1479092,"uid":129670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n 818一定要出嚟"},{"pid":"c31bd2e244a767256813ce56c3344c59e3ced97c","tid":1479092,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818 2點 維園見<br />\n大家一定要出！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a14Krun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa14Krun.jpg&h=f12c1c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkxLVot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkxLVot.jpg&h=9b3f8527&s={SIZE}\" /><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xg1EfoE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXg1EfoE.jpg&h=24a18478&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vynXB0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vynXB0.jpg&h=613c2f83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSvYvW0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSvYvW0.jpg&h=a8c38726&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRJLaW1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRJLaW1.jpg&h=c891df23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://